⚠️ Common Mistakes
19. Using multiple H1 headings is:

A. Recommended
B. Bad practice
C. Required
D. Faster

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: Only one H1 should exist per document.

20. Skipping H2 and jumping to H4:

A. Correct
B. Optimized
C. Incorrect
D. Required

✅ Answer: C
📘 Explanation: Breaks logical hierarchy.

21. Writing unclear headings leads to:

A. Better results
